OL,6,FSenior doctors at the Belfast Trust
OL,7,Fraised serious concerns about the
OL,8,Fculture within the organisation and
OL,9,Fits impact on staff wellbeing 18
OL,10,Fmonths ago, UTV can reveal.
OL,12,FThe doctors warned that some medics
OL,13,Fwere so upset by their treatment by
OL,14,Fmanagement that they were left feeling
OL,15,Fsuicidal.
