OL,3,CSenior doctors at Belfast Trust raised
OL,4,Cconcerns 18 months ago
OL,6,FThe claims were made during a meeting
OL,7,Fin January 2024 between a large number
OL,8,Fof doctors and consultants from across
OL,9,Fthe Belfast Trust and the
OL,10,Forganisation's former chairman Ciaran
OL,11,FMulgrew.
OL,13,FMr Mulgrew was not the subject of any
OL,14,Fof the concerns raised by the doctors
OL,15,Fand is understood to have raised these
OL,16,Fconcerns with trust management and the
OL,17,FDepartment of Health. He also held a
OL,18,Fnumber of follow-up meetings with the
OL,19,Fdoctors to try and address their
OL,20,Fconcerns about trust leadership.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
