OL,4,Cconcerns 18 months ago
OL,6,FDetails of the meeting were outlined
OL,7,Fin a follow up letter from the group
OL,8,Fto Mr Mulgrew.
OL,10,FThe letter, seen by UTV, mentioned how
OL,11,Fsome doctors were in tears during the
OL,12,Fmeeting as they outlined their
OL,13,Fexperiences.
OL,15,FThe correspondence also claimed there
OL,16,Fhad been "clear reference to suicidal
OL,17,Fideation amongst consultant staff" who
OL,18,Fhad been subjected to internal
OL,19,Fdisciplinary procedures, known as the
OL,20,FMaintaining High Professional
OL,21,FStandards process (MHPS).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
