OL,3,CSenior doctors at Belfast Trust raised
OL,4,Cconcerns 18 months ago
OL,6,FOne consultant told the meeting: "it
OL,7,Fis only by good fortune that we had
OL,8,Fnot had a colleague commit suicide due
OL,9,Fto the ordeal."
OL,11,FConcern was also raised "regarding the
OL,12,Fculture and perceived lack of
OL,13,Fpsychological safety in the
OL,14,Fenvironment in which consultant
OL,15,Fmedical staff work in the BHSCT and
OL,16,Ftheir experience of interactions with
OL,17,Fexecutive leadership within the
OL,18,Forganisation".
