OL,3,CSenior doctors at Belfast Trust raised
OL,4,Cconcerns 18 months ago
OL,6,FAllegations were also made in the
OL,7,Fletter that in some cases doctors were
OL,8,Fplaced under the disciplinary process
OL,9,Fafter "raising whistleblowing concerns
OL,10,Faround patient safety."
OL,12,FMr Mulgrew was asked to step down as
OL,13,Fchairman of the Belfast Trust last
OL,14,Fweek by the health minister, who said
OL,15,Fa fresh start was needed, however the
OL,16,Fmove has been met with unease amongst
OL,17,Fmembers of the Belfast Trust's medical
OL,18,Fstaff committee.
