OL,3,CSenior doctors at Belfast Trust raised
OL,4,Cconcerns 18 months ago
OL,6,FOne source told UTV that Mr Mulgrew
OL,7,Fhad been extremely supportive of their
OL,8,Fconcerns and proactive in addressing
OL,9,Fthem and raising them at the highest
OL,10,Flevels.
OL,12,FThe source added that committee
OL,13,Fmembers did not believe Mr Mulgrew
OL,14,Fshould have been the person to be
OL,15,Fasked to go and are concerned that his
OL,16,Freplacement will not be as supportive.
