OL,3,CSenior doctors at Belfast Trust raised
OL,4,Cconcerns 18 months ago
OL,6,FIn a statement the Belfast Trust said:
OL,7,F"Belfast Trust supports all staff who
OL,8,Fwish to tell us of their experiences
OL,9,Fand we have offered a number of
OL,10,Foptions for them to do so.
OL,12,F"We encourage staff to talk to us and
OL,13,Fwe also have a firm commitment to our
OL,14,Fwhistleblowing policy.
OL,16,F"We are providing bespoke training,
OL,17,Fand communicate daily with staff,
OL,18,Ffocusing on patient safety in addition
OL,19,Fto having dedicated weekly governance
OL,20,Fmeetings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
